print(greet())</pre></div>

python.python generators:
Generators are memory-efficient iterators defined with <strong>`yield`</strong>.<div class='responsediv'><pre># Generator example
def count_up_to(n):
    i = 1
    while i <= n:
        yield i
        i += 1

for num in count_up_to(3):
    print(num)</pre></div>

